<h1 class="post-title">About Us?</h1>

<h3 class="post-row-title" style="margin-bottom: 1em;">Welcome to By the Campfire</h3>

<p class="post-content" style="margin-bottom: 2em;">
    This is a multi-authored collection of random literature, stories, and musings by a close-knit group of friends,
    namely: Ned, Miguel, and Dwight. Ned decided to build this site since he knows the specific kind of "literature"
    required to put a web page together (coding).
    Here, you will read posts from the three of us (or more, if anyone wants to join!). We have all agreed to use our
    pen names rather than our real identities.
    If you'd like to join us around the bonfire, kindly disturb @ned and send him a message<a href="/join"
        style="color: var(--fire-main);"> by clicking
        this link.</a>
</p>

<h3 class="post-row-title" style="margin-bottom: 1em;">The Authors</h3>
<p class="post-content" style="margin-bottom: 1em;">
    We'd love to read yours, join us now!.
</p>

